    <h1>Spaghetti Carbonara</h1>
    <p>This classic Italian dish is simple, rich, and delicious.</p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Spaghetti</li>
      <li>Pancetta</li>
      <li>Eggs</li>
      <li>Parmesan cheese</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Boil the pasta.</li>
      <li>Cook the pancetta.</li>
      <li>Mix eggs and cheese.</li>
      <li>Combine everything off the heat.</li>
    </ol>

